genresAdvancedInfo.name: indie queretano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Indie queretano is a style of indie rock that originated in the Mexican state of Querétaro. It is characterized by its melodic guitar riffs, introspective lyrics, and dreamy, atmospheric soundscapes. Indie queretano bands often draw inspiration from their local culture and history, weaving traditional Mexican elements into their music.
